·惠特克|佛瑞斯·惠特克]]簽約參演，而[[麥可·斯圖巴|麥可·斯圖巴]]則於6月加入飾演一名[[CIA|CIA]]探員<ref name=WhitakerCast>{{cite news |last1=Kroll |first1=Justin |title=Forest Whitaker Eyes ‘Story of Your Life’ With Amy Adams (EXCLUSIVE) |url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/story-of-your-life-forest-whitaker-cast-amy-adams-1201464488/ |accessdate=2015-06-09 |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |date=2015-04-01 |archive-date=2015-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150616133558/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/story-of-your-life-forest-whitaker-cast-amy-adams-1201464488/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=White |first=James |title=Michael Stuhlbarg Joins Story Of Your Life |url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=44642 |accessdate=2015-06-20 |work=Empireonline |date=2015-06-17 |archive-date=2015-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150618100233/http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=44642 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。語言學教授{{link-en|謝茜嘉·庫恩|Jessica Coon}}被邀協助艾美·亞當斯飾演角色<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://scienceandfilm.org/articles/2802/alien-speak-linguist-dr-jessica-coon-on-villeneuves-arrival|title=Sloan Science & Film|website=scienceandfilm.org|access-date=2016-11-11|archive-date=2016-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161112040351/http://scienceandfilm.org/articles/2802/alien-speak-linguist-dr-jessica-coon-on-villeneuves-arrival|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 拍攝 ===
2015 年 6 月 7 日在[[加拿大|加拿大]][[魁北克|魁北克]]省的[[蒙特利爾|蒙特利爾]]<ref>{{cite news |title=On the Set for 6/8/15: Paul Feig & Melissa Mccarthy Start Shooting Ghostbusters, Ryan Reynolds Finishes Off Deadpool & More |url=http://www.ssninsider.com/on-the-set-for-6815-paul-feig-melissa-mccarthy-start-shooting-ghostbusters-ryan-reynolds-finishes-off-deadpool-more/ |accessdate=2015-06-09 |work=ssninsider.com |date=2015-06-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150610031021/http://www.ssninsider.com/on-the-set-for-6815-paul-feig-melissa-mccarthy-start-shooting-ghostbusters-ryan-reynolds-finishes-off-deadpool-more/ |archivedate=2015-06-10 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Amy Adams, Jennifer Garner spotted in Montreal as Hollywood filming heats up|url=http://montrealgazette.com/entertainment/local-arts/amy-adams-jennifer-garner-spotted-in-montreal-as-hollywood-filming-heats-up|work=[[蒙特婁憲報|Montreal Gazette]]|date=2015-06-07|accessdate=2016-09-10|archive-date=2015-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150712005833/http://montrealgazette.com/entertainment/local-arts/amy-adams-jennifer-garner-spotted-in-montreal-as-hollywood-filming-heats-up|dead-url=no}}</ref>，就在[[傑瑞米·雷納|傑瑞米·雷納]]完成《[[美國隊長3：英雄內戰|美國隊長3：英雄內戰]]》後開始拍摄<ref name="RennerCast" />。

電影劇本的語言使用了由藝人[[瑪蒂妮·貝特朗|瑪蒂妮·貝特朗]]<!--Martine Bertrand-->（美術指導{{link-en|帕特里斯·弗米特|Patrice Vermette}}的妻子），是根據劇本作者的原本概念。[[史蒂芬·沃爾夫勒姆|史蒂芬·沃爾夫勒姆]]及基斯杜化·沃爾夫勒姆分析了它來為電影中露薏絲的工作提供了基礎<ref>[https://www.wired.com/2016/11/arrivals-designers-crafted-mesmerizing-alien-alphabet/ How Arrival's Designers Crafted a Mesmerizing Language] {{Wayback|url=https://www.wired.com/2016/11/arrivals-designers-crafted-mesmerizing-alien-alphabet/ |date=20161116230232 }}. Margaret Rhodes, ''[[Wired_(magazine)|Wired]]''. November 16, 2016.</ref>。劇組諮詢了[[麥基爾大學|麥基爾大學]]的三位語言學家，而電影中的外星人聲音檔案是由[[語音學|語音學]]專家{{link-en|摩根‧松德|Morgan Sonderegger}}創建出來的。{{link-en|麗莎·特拉維斯|Lisa Travis}}被諮詢為主角的工作場所的設計。{{link-en|加拿大調查委員會|Canada Research Chair}}的{{link-en|謝茜嘉·庫恩|Jessica Coon}}，在語法和土著語言中，在劇本修訂和完成期間諮詢了她的[[语言学|語言學]]專業知識<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://montrealgazette.com/opinion/columnists/watchwords-denis-villeneuves-new-film-arrival-gets-to-the-heart-of-language|title=Watchwords: Denis Villeneuve's new film, Arrival, gets to the heart of language|last=Abley|first=Mark|date=2016-11-04|work=|newspaper=[[蒙特婁憲報|Montreal Gazette]]|8=|access-date=2017-01-05|via=|archive-date=2017-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106011350/http://montrealgazette.com/opinion/columnists/watchwords-denis-villeneuves-new-film-arrival-gets-to-the-heart-of-language|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 市場營銷 ==
首支預告片於2016年8月在網上釋出<ref>{{cite web|last1=Sharf|first1=Zack|title=‘Arrival’ Official Trailer: Amy Adams and Denis Villeneuve Make Alien Contact In Ambitious Sci-Fi Drama|url=http://www.indiewire.com/2016/08/arrival-trailer-amy-adams-denis-villeneuve-jeremy-renner-oscars-1201716795/|website=Indiewire|accessdate=2016-08-18|archive-date=2016-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160817221822/http://www.indiewire.com/2016/08/arrival-trailer-amy-adams-denis-villeneuve-jeremy-renner-oscars-1201716795/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[派拉蒙電影|派拉蒙影業]]發布了一系列幽浮登陸各國的海報來宣傳，其中一張是幽浮登陸於[[香港|香港]]，但圖中卻將[[上海|上海]]的[[東方明珠塔|東方明珠塔]]誤植在其中。這種錯誤引起了香港網友的不滿。派拉蒙發表聲明表示這都歸因於海報設計商[[BLT_Communications|BLT Communications]]的疏失<ref name="skylineblunder">{{cite news |title=Hong Kong outrage at 'Arrival' poster skyline blunder |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-37127909 |date=2016-08-19 |work=BBC |accessdate=2016-08-19 |archive-date=2016-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160820001245/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-37127909 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。之后，电影制作方再次发布了中国版的电影官方海报，但背景不再是香港的维港，而是把[[不明飞行物|UFO]]的降落地点彻底换在了上海的[[陆家嘴|陆家嘴]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20160819/bkn-20160819130003154-0819_00862_001_cn.html|title=《Arrival》海报火速更正 派拉蒙认错获赞|accessdate=2019-01-01|work=on.cc東網|language=zh-hk|archive-date=2019-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190102002207/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20160819/bkn-20160819130003154-0819_00862_001_cn.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

