estival-2016-lineup-full-list-1201811906/|dead-url=no}}</ref>與[[倫敦影展|倫敦影展]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://whatson.bfi.org.uk/lff/Online/default.asp?BOparam::WScontent::loadArticle::permalink=arrival|title=Arrival|website=BFI London Film Festival|accessdate=2016-09-01|archive-date=2016-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160925004951/https://whatson.bfi.org.uk/lff/Online/default.asp?BOparam::WScontent::loadArticle::permalink=arrival|dead-url=yes}}</ref>上展出。該片定於 2016 年 11 月 11 日在美國廣泛上映<ref>{{cite news|title=Denis Villeneuve’s ‘Story of Your Life’ Gets Possible New Title, UK Release Date|url=http://collider.com/denis-villeneuve-story-of-your-life-arrival/|accessdate=2016-09-10|archive-date=2016-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160920195100/http://collider.com/denis-villeneuve-story-of-your-life-arrival/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/06/arrival-release-date-amy-adams-sci-fi-movie-story-of-your-life-1201774351/|title=Paramount Dates Its Splashy Amy Adams Sci-Fi Tale ‘Arrival’ For Awards Season|website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|first=Patrick|last=Hipes|date=2016-06-16|accessdate=2016-06-16|archive-date=2016-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160618145520/http://deadline.com/2016/06/arrival-release-date-amy-adams-sci-fi-movie-story-of-your-life-1201774351/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據 412 條評論，新鮮度 94%，平均得分 8.41/10<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/arrival_2016 |title=Arrival (2016) |publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=2016-09-08 |archive-date=2019-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191122033411/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/arrival_2016 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] 得分81（滿分100），獲得一致好評<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/arrival | title=Arrival reviews | work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] | publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] | accessdate=2016-09-01 | archive-date=2016-09-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160906005531/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/arrival | dead-url=no }}</ref>。根據 [[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]] 調查，在A+至F間，觀眾的平均評價落在「B」<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |url=https://m.cinemascore.com |title=CinemaScore |work=cinemascore.com |accessdate=2020-09-21 |archive-date=2002-09-14 |archive-url=http://webarchive.loc.gov/all/20020914132118/https://www.cinemascore.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。主要受影評人稱讚劇情和細節上的精心安排，以及演員們的精彩演出。

=== 票房 ===
在美國，分析師估計《異星入境》能在首週末從兩千兩百間戲院中獲得1700萬美元的票房，儘管片商保守估計為 1200 萬至 1500 萬美元<ref name="preview">{{cite web |url=http://www.latimes.com/business/hollywood/la-fi-ct-movie-projector-20161107-story.html |title='Doctor Strange' to hold off 'Arrival' and 'Almost Christmas' at the box office |work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |accessdate=2016-11-09 |archive-date=2016-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161109011231/http://www.latimes.com/business/hollywood/la-fi-ct-movie-projector-20161107-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。週四晚上，電影從一千九百四十四間戲院中獲得 140 萬美元的票房<ref name="#2">{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4240&p=.htm |title='Doctor Strange' to Repeat at #1 as 'Arrival', 'Almost Christmas' & 'Shut In' Hit Theaters |work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |accessdate=2016-11-12 |archive-date=2016-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161113111150/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4240&p=.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。美國首週末獲得 2400 萬美元的票房，位居當週票房排名第三<ref name="#2"/>。

中国大陆获得 1.09 亿人民币。

